N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4205.9 - Ineligible employees

State Regulations

All persons holding or applying for occupational licenses
are forbidden to employ in any capacity in connection with their licensed
operations, any person determined or adjudged by the commission to be
ineligible for an occupational license. Notes
